[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ワルター",
		"romanized_name": "Walther",
		"model_path_hash": "9038662813217487255",
		"text": "リンデ祭当日に急遽、このような招集がかかるとは",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ。お茶会では久しぶりね、ワルター、ジェロン",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "まったくだ。こんな風にお茶会で集めるなんて、\n国の手に落ちてから一度もなかったな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "罪を償っている立場で、怪しげな行動は控える。\nそれが共通の認識だったはずだが？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あら、そんなに毛を逆立てちゃって。\n私って信用がないのね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "王国との取引をしたララはともかく、\nお前やアンチュもいまだ要注意対象だろう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ワルター",
		"romanized_name": "Walther",
		"model_path_hash": "9038662813217487255",
		"text": "私は今、国からの指令が数多く舞い込み、\n非常に多忙で、充実しています",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ワルター",
		"romanized_name": "Walther",
		"model_path_hash": "9038662813217487255",
		"text": "とはいえ、先輩にも恩があります。\n先輩の無茶振りは、できるだけ対応しますが……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ワルター",
		"romanized_name": "Walther",
		"model_path_hash": "9038662813217487255",
		"text": "あまりに過激なのは勘弁願いますよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "俺もすでに王国に忠誠を誓った身。\n離反を疑われるような悪ふざけはできないぞ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ。本気で警戒されていますわよ、クリセルダ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ。それが錬金党だものね。\n懐かしいわ、この感覚……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "でも今日招いたのは、リンデ祭を一緒に祝いたかった\n……いえ、祝ってほしかったからなの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "今まで、そしていつもありがとう、ってね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "これはジェロンと弟くんに",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "毛並みを整える精油を調合してみたの。\n獣化の呪いで傷んでしまっているでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "あ、ああ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ワルター、これを受け取ってちょうだい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ワルター",
		"romanized_name": "Walther",
		"model_path_hash": "9038662813217487255",
		"text": "おお。どれも貴重な素材ではないですか！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふふ。集めるのに苦労したのよ？\n研究の役に立つんじゃないかしら？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ワルター",
		"romanized_name": "Walther",
		"model_path_hash": "9038662813217487255",
		"text": "ええ、もちろんです！\nわざわざ探してくる時間と手間が省けましたよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "本当に現金……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ララにはこれを。手荒れ防止になると思うわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あら。気付かれてしまいましたか。\n王の佇まいに隙があってはいけませんのに",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あなたは自ら働く王だもの。\n恥ではないし、時には手だって荒れるわよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そういうことでしたら、ありがたく。\nあなたの調合でしたら、効果は抜群ですわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "それから……アンチュには、これを",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "……ネックレス？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "私のとお揃いで作ったの。私のアンチュには、\nいつも私を身近に感じてほしいから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "うん……うん！　嬉しい……ありがとう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "極夜の錬金党党首として、みんなには改めて感謝を",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "あなたたちのおかげで、私はパルメ族の存在を\n表舞台に引きずり出すという本懐を遂げられた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "その過程で、あなたたちの存在は\n私の心の支えになってくれていた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "クリセルダ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "それぞれの渇望で結ばれた絆だけれど、\n私にはかけがえのない時間だった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "今まで――ありがとう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "それぞれ新たな渇望のために動いている今、\n錬金党はもう、役割を終えたわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ク、クリセルダ……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ずっと正式には言えなかったけれど……\n極夜の錬金党党首として、最後に伝えるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ここで……極夜の錬金党を解散する",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ワルター・マン",
		"romanized_name": "Walther Mann",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "研究者肌の錬金術士で、元「極夜の錬金党」。\n現在は国の監視下で、研究や調査に協力している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]